Package model

Interface PetShopModel

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
PetShopModelManager
public interface PetShopModel extends Serializable
Interface representing the Pet Shop Model. It provides methods to manage customers, animals, reservations, and purchases.
Version:
1.0 - December 2024
Author:
Martin Skovby Andersen, Rasmus Duus Kristensen, Victor Grud Oksen, Victor Sander Marx Hoelgaard
